title: Typographica's "Favorite Fonts of 2005 - Part 1"
content:
Typographica published their list -- [Our Favorite Fonts of 2005 Part 1](http://web.archive.org/web/20140805022009/http:/typographi.com/001045.php)

author: Norbert Florendo
